headline.print_headline: Cleveland Browns Wide Receiver Bess Arrested in Florida
headline.main: Cleveland Browns Wide Receiver Bess Arrested in Florida

lead_paragraph: Cleveland Browns wide receiver Davone Bess was arrested on Friday at an airport in Florida and charged with assaulting a police officer, officials said.
